{"tid":755914,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖)KFC個芝士撈通原來可以醫病","createTime":"2018-07-25T15:01:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T16:42:23.000Z","uid":170660,"like":6,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f22c1b28f6494e1537e3ad4420558b7fef3631e4","tid":755914,"uid":170660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T15:01:21.000Z","msg":"話說今朝起身已經feel到病病地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拿拿臨睇完醫生就返屋企諗住食藥休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n丫...醒起未買野食喎 就call咗老母叫佢買啲野食上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 佢倨然買咗KFC上黎<br />\n心諗：「病左點食呀大佬」跟手就拎左唯一食得既通粉黎食<br />\n<img src=\"https://cfcdn2.azsg.opensnap.com/azsg/snapphoto/photo/LD/GVY5/3C36TRA15D4529DB16EC6Blv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcfcdn2.azsg.opensnap.com%2Fazsg%2Fsnapphoto%2Fphoto%2FLD%2FGVY5%2F3C36TRA15D4529DB16EC6Blv.jpg&h=239a8126&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點知一食就停唔到手，啲芝士多到，啲料又足<br />\n食完一啖又一啖，好快就食哂<br />\n估唔到KFC都有啲咁好食既野 仲係做緊23蚊 (記得只可以跟餐 唔可以用其他食物轉)<br />\n<br />\n再食埋藥訓左一陣,而家好返哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n未試過既巴打真係可以食下 真心推介!!!"},{"pid":"72fca51c1b1c3ef9dc52a653d279991267bb3108","tid":755914,"uid":176166,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T15:02:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8156ca51b20a582bdcc970bf226802231781c2d1","tid":755914,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T15:02:44.000Z","msg":"咁啱感冒<br />\n聽日試"},{"pid":"30ec09c655d89411aef4ece88c3c3390613b3b28","tid":755914,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T15:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb90bd82c399534f9b977fe5824e504fdbc6b80","tid":755914,"uid":60982,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T15:04:31.000Z","msg":"佢d下午茶餐真係幾抵食<img src=\"/assets